{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","blocks":{"heading":{"type":"text","name":"Title","settings":{"text":"<h1>{{ closest.page.title }}<\/h1>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"center","type_preset":"h2","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["heading"],"settings":{"content_direction":"column","gap":32,"color_scheme":"scheme-5","padding-block-start":40,"padding-block-end":80}},"section_8YgMfC":{"type":"section","blocks":{"text_hLK7aV":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h2>Methods of Customization<\/h2>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_XJgzw3":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Jah and Co has specefic methods when it comes to customizing products we offer. <\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"divider_HAcEP8":{"type":"_divider","name":"t:names.divider","settings":{"thickness":1,"corner_radius":"square","width_percent":100,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_jbYyM8":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h2>Standard Customization<\/h2>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_VhfDbk":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Our normal customization service includes us creating a special design specefically for you. The design we create is based on your personality, style and vibe. <\/p><p>In order for us to learn tat specefic information, we ask for you to complete the Style Survey. This short survey ask a few general questions thatthat's allows us to leaarlearn more about you. We'll create a personalized experience from your reponsees. <\/p><p>Completing the survey will sign you up for email and or text marketing, which you may occaissionally receive emails\/ texts that may advertise specefic products made just for you. Additionally you'll receive special offers, discounts, new products alerts, and much more.<\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_hmFdFx":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h2>How to start an custom order<\/h2>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_YzDbnx":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>To get started on a custom order, head to the Custom Apparel page and locate the \"Custom Shirt Request\" product and then place an order with the product. <\/p><p>After placing your order you'll receive an email (not the confirmation order email) within the same or next day. <\/p><p>*If no email is received within 24hours please contact us*<\/p><p>The email is from us which we'll be in direct contact with you to get started with the customization process. *Please respond to any email from us in a timely manner*<\/p><p>When we complete the design(s), you'll receive an providing you with the completed designs which you'll be asked to approve or reject. You can also provide any feedback and assist us with any inspiration you may have to guide us. <\/p><p>If you choose to reject, we'll create another design or you can choose to cancel the whole process.<\/p><p>If you accept, you'll then receive a invoice email shortly. (pricing will be discussed during the process). Order will be processed once invoice is payed. <\/p><p>Processing may take 1-3 days upon payment. <\/p><p><\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_Xcq4Fe":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h2>Shirts with front designs <\/h2>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_yDMCqH":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>There may be some products with a design only on the front of shirt. These shirts have the option for you to add any design from our Design gallery to the back. <\/p><p>Check our the Design Gallery to view our created designs <\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_wiKHjL":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h2>Other Customization options<\/h2>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_xaeRx8":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Other options for customization may include the ability to add text, numbers or modify the colors of any shirt that has a design already. Customization options will be specified in the description for applicable products. <\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_FAYBFF":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h2>Customization for large groups or ocassions<\/h2>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_hzLCiA":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Purchases for large groups, events, occasions and anything related should contact us directly. <\/p><p>These purchases have the ability to present a design of your own to be displayed onto our products.<\/p><p>*Currently only these purchases can present there own design*<\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_hLK7aV","text_XJgzw3","divider_HAcEP8","text_jbYyM8","text_VhfDbk","text_hmFdFx","text_YzDbnx","text_Xcq4Fe","text_yDMCqH","text_wiKHjL","text_xaeRx8","text_FAYBFF","text_hzLCiA"],"n